  ('ph_001','rainy-cardero','vancouver-street','Rainy morning, Cardero','Coal Harbour side street, wet pavement reflection, low grey light.','Empty rain-soaked side street in downtown Vancouver at dawn with reflections of building lights on the pavement.','Fujifilm X-T4','XF 23mm f/2 R WR',400,'f/4.0','1/250s',23,'2026-01-14T07:42:00Z','/placeholders/ph_001.svg',1600,1067,'nebular-placeholder-svg','In-house editorial placeholder generated by Nebular Labs for the portfolio scaffold.','Aditya Chinchure (original Unsplash reference)','https://unsplash.com/photos/ZhQCZjr9fHo',array['street','vancouver','rain','morning'],true),
  ('ph_002','downtown-geometry','vancouver-street','Downtown geometry','Midday architecture, West Georgia. Glass, shadow, diagonal.','A downtown Vancouver office tower from street level, cropped into strong diagonal lines of glass and shadow.','Fujifilm X-T4','XF 35mm f/1.4 R',200,'f/5.6','1/1000s',35,'2026-01-21T13:15:00Z','/placeholders/ph_002.svg',1600,1067,'nebular-placeholder-svg','In-house editorial placeholder generated by Nebular Labs.','Mike Benna (original Unsplash reference)','https://unsplash.com/photos/Nh3P1t-yBvg',array['street','vancouver','architecture','geometry'],true),
  ('ph_003','seawall-solitary','coal-harbour-waterfront','Seawall, solitary','Single walker, low tide, North Shore mountains at dawn.','A single figure walking the Coal Harbour seawall with the North Shore mountains in soft dawn light.','Fujifilm X-T4','XF 56mm f/1.2 R',160,'f/2.8','1/500s',56,'2026-02-03T06:58:00Z','/placeholders/ph_003.svg',1600,1067,'nebular-placeholder-svg','In-house editorial placeholder generated by Nebular Labs.','Mike Benna (original Unsplash reference)','https://unsplash.com/photos/kSvpIjSgAw4',array['waterfront','seawall','coal-harbour','dawn'],true),
  ('ph_004','harbour-blue-hour','coal-harbour-waterfront','Harbour, blue hour','Inner harbour seaplane moorage, late winter, city lights waking.','The Coal Harbour seaplane moorage at blue hour with a seaplane silhouette and downtown city lights behind.','Fujifilm X-T4','XF 16-55mm f/2.8 R LM WR',800,'f/4.0','1/60s',35,'2026-02-12T17:30:00Z','/placeholders/ph_004.svg',1600,1067,'nebular-placeholder-svg','In-house editorial placeholder generated by Nebular Labs.','Mike Benna (original Unsplash reference)','https://unsplash.com/photos/KgZLxc5MeQU',array['waterfront','blue-hour','vancouver','seaplane'],true),
  ('ph_005','lagos-market-light','documentary-lagos','Market light, Lagos','Open-air fabric stalls under midday sun. Colour field study.','An open-air market in Lagos with a range of fabric stalls, bright daylight falling through canopy gaps onto the stacks of textiles.','Fujifilm X-T4','XF 23mm f/2 R WR',200,'f/5.6','1/800s',23,'2026-02-20T12:10:00Z','/placeholders/ph_005.svg',1600,1067,'nebular-placeholder-svg','In-house editorial placeholder generated by Nebular Labs.','Tope A. Asokere (original Unsplash reference)','https://unsplash.com/photos/wWz9fX4U6Pg',array['documentary','lagos','market','colour'],true),
